title: John Denver Discography Part 1
description:
It&#039;s about time John Denver got cleaned up. This is Part 1 of hopefully a fairly complete &#039;new set of files&#039; to replace the old ones that have existed for a time.

A fairly comprehensive (it&#039;s all been downloaded and searched through) replacement set, if all the parts get uploaded!

And yes - new stuff to make it even better!

PART 1

A single by Robert Schumann that was included in "at large" as a tribute to John Denver.
The Mitchell Trio tracks from the singles assortied stuff. (PLEASE UPLOAD ANY MITCHELL TRIO STUFF YOU HAVE!)
------ and yes, that&#039;s all that&#039;s unique in the entire &#039;singles&#039; (assortied and atlarge) stuff. [No, I am NOT uploading &#039;Good Morning Starshine&#039;]
